name: Oculian Basic Package
desc: A set blueprints that enables shipyards to assemble basic Oculian hulls ranging from the basic frigate carriers to moderately equipped cruiser schools.

name: Oculian General Package
desc: A set blueprints that enables shipyards to assemble modern Oculian hulls ranging from the phasic frigates to gargantuan capital class carriers.

name: Oculian Weapons Package
desc: This design chip is comprised of the uncommon Oculian weapon configurations normally being sold off to pirate markets.

name: Base Industry Blueprint
desc: Contains the technological specifications needed to construct a planet-side industry or structure.
